description:
It’s all coming up roses on this week’s episode of Unqualified as Anna and Sim hang out with former NFL player, philanthropist, and current star of ABC’s The Bachelor…Colton Underwood!

On today’s Tuesday episode, Colton, Anna, and Sim get into…

  • Football culture and the NFL
  • The inside scoop on being The Bachelor
  • Relationships and Colton’s Dating Deal-Breakers
  • Social media and the ‘fame bubble’

Catch Colton on The Bachelor every Monday on ABC!

And don’t forget to tune in Thursday to hear Anna and Colton chat with callers!

 

 

Follow us!
